斯外长的会晤中发誓要深化与莫斯科的关系。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;涌向北京的外交交通突显了国际参与者悄悄但日益增长的期望，即习近平应该在平息陷入更深冲突的世界&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/aH-UGTgqbxGjMNW-QiOy6TKiSC1Lwp6SvtpeX3d3PF-YDiyTuwmS3vWBlNP6cGVdRUCl3col4NzHz1va_qlwCdqhTrAstLk53Ib3YvzGY7CIWfV_cenhG_1SO3YIFD0ANeS1wMQoc2F0VNPrpsJvGe9EQCSuCavkJ1DHz2g50aXgNJI_3kR6wqM2BkpBK2JtjRCHaizpM8i6G0MLLjwI5DwA-sW20cdRugl1N3MeAyp-5f_1GnLM2UB_w3_X2o9BLh6XhY1qBWyizhAI1N7DEzKbcwgidmqLEbhbQKjRxKeOdXTu1vIZ6TqG7hVvXoR-itaDby6trO7C5O09ACmN21-dTGGWhfUTHakGdj1ldQe5OHkF0Jhft6MvggM142xbAfveRE8MIpjgFWYASwgJvn7OrPej-p_PK_XYq_sjUQQGutAS906S4QKJ-AE_ufpgkGAt1XC78lMtPdZsdGdN8oQTp3cylTFmcq7Uj4I0xPK7qUsm6ov3NFCfJpXAD7nlSNXR-mwT-5IxsXBJ0xLhT0c/jfn-qvSMEx9BqK6ZpJn0loNnZgjs-lVw/19" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="中国王毅敦促谈判维持脆弱的伊朗与美国停火"&gt;方面发挥更积极的作用&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;唐纳德·特朗普总统让他作为稳定力量的潜力得到了极大的释放，他花了一周&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/ZQoYdS8OUTo7Hk8EJLQGKM3Mvf8xP1eBlK8_ZGlJSqUWDxSAMi2POlZ0OLjOG9LgNM5kd8XE1_aub1Ve05EU7PAUF1M8t2Os3oD6mmAsm7U36MPbduyd4PqUmvopxEvnA21k1a5rGxSVMPfNAq4gXNd2JEYiZ9kTfP_qfVkz1K2DRfhUm4T_IWIPZXwmNIqeOFBHTNae4ea3Mx_hAx9swj490wUH9mUgvZJntlXTghz3VLuMx6N4neHkm6cawO5GReOrn1BEh2pvaJSWMDfiuNLlSt6fWGDbPcrlzifp4ZQvcNXt7yIA0iAJxhJ2qPandBB4wciud5rB29oSyKRYI0lTWArXQ5owP3vN-eEkHHX9O8H3m-tiO5Bkfxyg2SiZ1g8OUIhy9CVtl-sLxBXRMaZgO0C32hMJIDyK-Lm1hAf752lS-bjrFNrSINsRAkDKWv4S0VV0-3YfnjoNBCOjSNiRrH-Srlsipy5R_0GwE_z8NXOj864ldy_cz3Nbc3qTXZwWAylvPZbhlAQxqNRf/eRyWy6obA060853ZwYZdvEepUk6SGNCK/19" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="贝森特和英国首相里夫斯在会面前就伊朗战争问题存在分歧"&gt;的时间斥责英国和意大利的曾经的盟友&lt;/a&gt;，更不用说美国教皇了。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;但迄今为止，习近平的外交努力还未能与其他地方推进的更具体举措相提并论。法国和英国正在就开放霍尔木兹海峡的航运问题&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/sXg3oHS0QWa4KCxDPwTexn-lx5k7nJg-2rlCpzUF32wm_E4W-4iM7gnRtRzXS