e.bloomberg.com/a/sc/iwn1P8wWlXzz29MmyTm3wc9mt0Zr-tp5KZRW9xCgiU9PJnfrT4kQqCxq8fLN3jEARn5sZJM_Bi-anZyKmV-NCRzSzk1QLw5Vh_yik3yftv_gePy1SYShCnhP4pWiUG5JBbZXpq0HrIJvCBbS4CGc3fBl4GNkFQ6yjKeju19HexrHMRAYUP7wsx1hK99uC_v4Mtkn0bk1My8Qh4zCznWjIGacqdFq-AEC7mutP67XChfv-Q5Oiqxwn6Z8DrVeQyhOdieQ-w15kCITqSZGGPAqbb0kCSJePU32AZwuAxmjT4rUcy3PIOFMtEyJmfmUIov5ZVFZ8_QBB-XgBc2MY6pUMgie0wyqezpJiV-qAQE0aG_KPNpBTEBo06mhwJTXZ-JeeRl4OCqiKqxMrPBDW_fhLq049DEBM64Lxd1Sbe5QO0K7PpBH8SuHl-CX-d2_2Al-KpiAijsCD-OgsUwChPlCVjkMKP6_vfxxvIpOGPKkqOEWdebwiY3RBuJOvtMYZBizGYt0LP6qPLUqgueGjOUlVw/zDdhAFmKiF5kAyXha48FgEhTiXozt92B/19" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="不到 10,000 票分裂秘鲁有希望争夺决选权的人"&gt;微弱优势，&lt;/a&gt;与藤森惠子展开角逐，尽管数十万张有争议的选票可能会将最终结果推迟数周。这一结果可能决定铜出口国能否最终打破长达数年的政治不稳定周期。 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;figure style="margin: 20px 0;"&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;table width="580"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iM9Rr6Q.lU28/v10/-1x-1.jpg" alt="Roberto Sanchez, presidential candidate for the Together for Peru party, center, during a news conference at the party&amp;amp;#39;s headquarters in Lima, Peru, on Sunday, April 12, 2026. The lack of a clear opponent against the Popular Force party&amp;amp;#39;s Keiko Fujimori means it’s still uncertain whether Peru’s runoff will feature two candidates from the right or become a more ideological battle with a leftist rival. Photographer: Marco Garro&amp;amp;#x2F;Bloomberg" width="580"/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;div style="display:none"&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;img alt="2026 年 4 月 12 日星期日，秘鲁团结党总统候选人罗伯托·桑切斯（中）在秘鲁利马该党总部举行的新闻发布会上。人民力量党的藤森庆子缺乏明确的对手，这意味着秘鲁的决选是否会由两名右翼候选人组成，还是会成为与左翼对手的一场意识形态较量，目前仍不确定。摄影师：Marco Garro&amp;amp;#x2F;Bloomberg" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iM9Rr6Q.lU28/v10/-1x-1.jpg" style="width: 100%; display: block; margin-bottom: 4px;" /&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;figcaption&gt;&lt;div style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4;"&gt;桑切斯周日在利马。&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/figcaption&gt;&lt;div style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4; font-style: italic;"&gt;摄影师：Marco Garro/彭博社&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;彼得·马扎尔 (Péter Magyar) 已经&lt;/strong&gt;做出了许多人认为不可想象的事情，即在 16 年后将维克托·欧尔班 (Viktor Orban) 赶下匈牙利的权力，现在面临着推翻他的非自由制度的更大挑战&lt;strong style="font-size: 16px;"&gt; &lt;/strong&gt;特朗普和欧洲民族主义者的榜样。马扎尔的新贵蒂萨党在选举中取得压倒性胜利，获得了绝对多数席位，马扎尔有机会&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/XTmdFmI2xDXh2u6yr-wX0lf4Dw88ST_sviatvGz551dSpAh9RU2ms0GUexk_l27bqYVqWDDQeBK0ss-1hHplcgJ6ra97znIS23RKTMkOFOSvEcvi-07QPPsttn6pGhPhTbp05mxPxtkUbJfhFBZ-Y3dAbKoBgpu9gVE5cN4Lp6cyXEgjn35ltEcThvRB2VZGATnh8cngcsX5RFE80nfyom29SfwDLiooIH6iJ9nMvE7tOKxntXT6Xc5vKCGTyMPXSB2AJS-stuDUDP7HpiWyOLgqHewL--eWQMfgVXEFwyCdsHlRICJpU4gA5-5s8cBy5bvkDnrwDnvfA3Ef5YxjQJneBOIWbROFgWoacDixwWnhE7pZI7uys6jGVXqTY08yDWVb4THIsiuVRTOI8g7L5EdZzYbPgcBNQvWP__hW7w_BULESzbnBw9KwR42TGfFUgXUiGeGD4kBp3woF_3F55lfQxx8SWVsYYt45wGC-cw7PayYmmAsCgQmkdkyamtrLucfmcs-kzPEy444/7yzs7dsDcf4EiTLLXlv_ktnGFn6b_jlA/19" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="推翻欧尔班在匈牙利根深蒂固的制度并不容易"&gt;消灭欧尔班主义&lt;/a&gt;本身。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;总统候选人帕洛玛·瓦伦西亚&lt;/strong&gt;表示，哥伦比亚应将石油和天然气重新置于其能源政策的中心位置，并呼吁通过&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/JKCg3SKuN1UGGyFbjWBiLh84GDmITvKBuXtsaXoIq0loJ7ZM0wbl1dzM8x7xvvJXU3EZ42qRPQmz--Ncd0Uv9vz_fzNQzme6oKESKZqldFJUrgxHaXmEncHW1lbpxD11rck2sgYRzI07L3GR6QyahyCsq3yWcdoDmt_UiikaGBTHqdkuCfjQ8_nhXav5gw_YlKSIwJkI5BfR3w9LxR69DmMCdkez57QwBUnrUQGze993K0I9GoYjpJU0IzO0FBXszHaoGMBPk5pi-kIuVEd-u8JT8o9Uj2vdO0RpfiCIZKvdfhFd3avZcHG6U6NtJK7i7Q7GPNHBpd-1xGvEq9gP2ViiVDBBTC_x2CZHSv_8OISRJwr-Uf_JjDZ-NFbPSPHcaQNr6OnthnrPA_Gn80YgV5MXmq9i8IyaqDAHSYKecFeWe4CjTigrNNNjBZpNNYUoHgtelHVzDwk4SjyLLI-sfWNOvxt1F_GG9jpFg9C430seFVJ22uxC40mQa-T29NAAlkhuwKHOU3WJCMkFF6m